rooms.Name: Above the Mountain of Norn
rooms.Description:
You are surrounded by a dark hazy mist as you begin to fly above the great
mountain of Norn and feel a chilling cold to your very bones as the wind
whips around you.

rooms.Name: In the Air
rooms.Description:
Surrounded by nothing but clouds you float and fly higher and higher until
even the great mountain of Norn is but a tiny spec on the plains of the frost
giants.

rooms.Name: Further in the Air
rooms.Description:
The Clouds surrounding you seem to gain substance and you hear the sound of
music coming from one just east of here.  Perhaps the birds voices are
stronger here where the wind whips you about like a feather, but that sounds
an awful like drums and not whistles.

rooms.Name: The Pentagram Chamber
rooms.Description:
This room surrounds you with the smell of burning flesh and rotten eggs...you
only wish that those glowing red eyes at the center weren't your fate to face
as you move forward to face Diablo himself...but only you can stop diablo
from waking the mighty Ragnarok to destroy Midgaard prepare yourself for the
end.

rooms.Name: Diablo's Lair
rooms.Description:
Not that you'll have time to read this but the great master of the undead the
sentient being of all evil the plotter of all destruction the Really big
REally bad REAlly mean REALly ugly REALLy furious REALLY KILLING YOU Diablo
is here!
